

install cpan using 
curl -L https://cpanmin.us | perl - -M https://cpan.metacpan.org -n Mojolicious 
then
cpan  modulename
cpan SQL::Translator
cpan Mojolious
 
cpan DBIx::Class::Migration
cpan Mojolicious::Plugin::Bcrypt
cpan Plack 
cpan DBIx::Class::InflateColumn::Boolean
cpan DBIx::Class::InflateColumn::Currency
cpan Math::Round
cpan HTTP::Server::PSGI
cpan Plack

finaly 
plackup script/moblo

navigate to 127.0.0.1:5000 on your machine

to test just open up browser console and type start_test();
